Fig. 2 is a schematic view of producing the cigarette using the cigarette paper of the present invention.

claim.claim-text:
A method for manufacturing a cigarette paper with a fire retardant strip, characterizing in that: the method comprises the following steps:
forming a film-forming material solution by dissolving a film-forming material into solvent under high speed dispersion;
forming a fire retardant by adding a filling material into the film-forming material solution under high speed dispersion;
forming a fire retardant strip by printing the fire retardant on a front side and/or back side of cigarette base paper using a printer.
